==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incoördination
<hw>In`co*⟦oum⟧r`di*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Lack
of co⟦oum⟧rdination; lack of harmonious adjustment or action.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Inco⟦oum⟧rdination of muscular movement</b></col>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld>, <cd>irregularity in movements resulting from
inharmonious action of the muscles in consequence of loss of voluntary
control over them.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incoronate</ent>⟦br⟧
